sequenceDiagram
    participant Saga as Order Saga
    participant Inv as Inventory
    participant Pay as Payment
    participant Ship as Shipping

    Saga->>Inv: 1. Reserve Stock
    Inv-->>Saga: Stock Reserved

    Saga->>Pay: 2. Charge Payment
    Pay-->>Saga: Payment Failed!

    Note over Saga: Compensation begins

    Saga->>Inv: 3. Release Stock (compensate)
    Inv-->>Saga: Stock Released

    Saga->>Saga: Report failure to user
